data.eml:eml: Two new feather mites of the genus Neocalcealges Orwig (Analgoidea: Trouessartiidae) from the Sichuan province of China

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Wang, Zi-Ying, Proctor, Heather (2015): Two new feather mites of the genus Neocalcealges Orwig (Analgoidea: Trouessartiidae) from the Sichuan province of China.
